  "helpSealsBody": "Every verse has three difficulty levels: Seal I (bronze, slow), Seal II (silver, faster) and Seal III (gold, very fast). Seal II unlocks once you've earned at least 2 stars on Seal I — Seal III unlocks the same way after 2 stars on Seal II.",
  "helpStarsTitle": "Stars",
  "helpStarsBody": "Seals I and II offer up to 3 stars: 3 stars for a flawless run, 2 stars for at most 2 mistakes, otherwise 1 star for finishing. Seal III awards a single master star on success.",
